## Saved Views

### Creating a Saved View

If supported:

1. Configure your filters
1. Click **Save View**
1. Name the view
1. Use later with one click

### Saved View Contents

Views save:

- City filter
- Campaign name filter
- Lead status filter
- Latest state filter
- Sort preference (lead or distance)
- Search text and mode
- Structured query filters
- Custom field filters
- Column visibility settings
- Page size

### Managing Views

- Reorder views via drag-and-drop
- Delete views you no longer need
- Exit saved view to return to default

## Clearing Filters

### Reset All

Clear all filters at once:

1. Click **Reset** or **Clear Filters**
1. All filters removed
1. Full list displays

### Clear Individual

Remove one filter:

1. Click the X on the filter chip
1. Or uncheck the option
1. Other filters remain

