## Troubleshooting

### No Results Found

If search returns nothing:

1. Check spelling
1. Broaden filters
1. Clear all filters to verify data exists
1. Try different search terms
1. Check search mode (simple vs structured)

### Too Many Results

If results are overwhelming:

1. Add more filters
1. Use more specific search terms
1. Use structured query for precision

### Structured Query Errors

If query has errors:

1. Check syntax (Field OPERATOR "Value")
1. Verify field name is valid
1. Quote values properly
1. Don't mix AND/OR

### AI Search Not Working

If AI search fails:

1. System falls back to simple search automatically
1. Try structured query instead
1. Check network connection

